 a focus on specialty retail and enterprise softwareDemonstrated experience selling or implementing retail technology solutions such as POS, CRM, WMS, ERP, or related systemsDemonstrated success building and scaling distributor and VAR networks while also managing or closely aligning with direct sales teams.Deep understanding of the retail operations, including POS, store systems, omnichannel retail processes, SAAS modelsStrong deal‑making skills: negotiation, executive communication, and the ability to unlock complex multi‑stakeholder enterprise deals.Arabic fluency is an advantageComfortable operating in a remote, high‑growth, target‑driven environment with frequent cross‑time‑zone collaboration.\nLocation and travelThe role is remote with regular travel to partners, customers, and events, depending on territory coverage and partner footprint.\nWhat We Offer:Competitive compensation and performance-based incentivesFlexible remote working environment.Opportunity to shape global channel growth for a leading retail platform.Collaborative, growth-focused company culture."}
