rsation - not scripts or pressure tactics• Work remotely with full support from our Athens headquarters\nWe’re not looking for cold-callers or lead-chasers. We’re looking for trusted connectors.\nWho Our Clients Are\n• Entrepreneurs, business owners, and investors with €250,000–€800,000+ to invest• Self-made successes who built wealth through talent and persistence• Often from environments where institutions have failed them - they’re sceptical for good reason• Looking for optionality: security, Schengen access, European education, and peace of mind for their families• They value relationships over transactions and won’t be rushed or pressured\nOur clients need someone who understands their world, respects their scepticism, and guides with patience and honesty.\nWhat We’re Looking For\nEssential:\n• Existing relationships with HNWIs in UAE• Cultural fluency - you genuinely understand the communities you’d serve• Fluent English (written and verbal)• Comfortable with commission-only compensation• Integrity - you’d rather lose a deal than mislead someone\nHighly Desirable:\n• Experience in real estate, immigration, wealth management, or financial services• Active LinkedIn presence\nBackgrounds that often do well:\n• Business owners and entrepreneurs• Private bankers and wealth managers• Lawyers and accountants serving affluent clients• Real estate professionals in investment or luxury markets• Community leaders and well-connected professionals\nWhat You Get\n• Full training and certification on our programmes - no cost to you• Access to our curated property portfolio (60+ vetted developments across Athens)• Psychological messaging framework and conversation guides designed for high-stakes, trust-based advisory - not generic sales scripts• CRM system for pipeline management• Branded marketing materials and property documents ready to share with clients• Direct support from our Athens headquarters - legal coordination, transaction management, and immigration filing handled for you• As we grow together, you’ll receive warm leads from our marketing campaigns alongside your own network\nOur Values\nFreedom - The right to become who you are capable of becoming - unconstrained by the circumstances of your birth.\nIntegrity - Not a character trait - an infrastructure. We engineer trustworthiness into every process.\nPartnership - We build relationships, not transactions. We stay with clients long after the permit is approved."}
