, tool use (function calling), streaming responses, batch processing, and model selection across Claude Opus, Sonnet, and Haiku variants for cost and latency optimisation Familiarity with enterprise connectors and integrations within Claude ecosystem including Microsoft 365 (Outlook, Teams, SharePoint), browser automation via Claude in Chrome, and third party MCP connectors for operational data sources Understanding of AI safety, security, and governance principles including prompt injection defence, content filtering, data privacy controls, audit logging, and compliance with enterprise security policies when deploying AI agents at scale\n\nContinuous learning in AI, LLMs, and automation expected."}
