ning, lead times, MOQs, incoterms, freight, and customsHands-on experience managing 3PLs and fulfillment operations, ideally including Amazon FBAStrong experience managing suppliers, production timelines, QA standards, and factory negotiationsStrong systems mindset with experience building scalable workflows and operational processesExperience using operational tools such as Monday.com and Google Drive to structure workflows and documentationAbility to build demand and inventory forecasts and translate them into purchasing and production plansStrong leadership capability with experience managing managers and cross-functional teamsStrong communication and decision-making ability in fast-moving environmentsFluent in English\nDO NOT APPLY IF:\nIf any of these resonate with you, please do NOT apply.\nClock-in / clock-out mindsetLow ownership and needs constant supervisionIntegrity is flexible under pressureHides problems and avoids transparencyDefensive, rigid, ego-drivenComfort > growthHates processes + structureAvoids hard decisions\nAPPLY IF:\nIf you resonate with all of these, we encourage you to apply.\nEnergized by $30m → $500mExtreme ownershipRadical transparencyFast-movingHigh standards, low egoBuilds structure that scalesWants real impactIntegrity under pressureGrowth mindset\nIf this sounds like you, we’d love to hear from you.\nPlease apply via this link: https://forms.gle/GWdmkBPgTRMRxUwm8"}
