CloudKnowledge of one or more competitive products and technologies such as BitDefender, Xena, XM-Cyber, TREX, etc.Experience working with some of the solutions from Ixia Security related Technology Partners, such as Palo Alto, Fortinet, Cisco, Checkpoint, Riverbed, Dynatrace, FireEye, Extrahop, ForcePoint, ForeScout etc.Excellent initiative and ability to align broad strategic and tactical goalsGreat customer facing skills; builds credibility and confidence in Ixia’s service offeringsCollaborative and cross functional style works with sales, development and marketing teams to aid in growing services business.Expertise in Wireshark, other testing productsPractical trouble-shooter of complex technical problemsExcellent presentation skills and the ability to present NAS solutions and new technologies at trade shows/conferences etc.Good written and verbal communication skillsTeamwork spiritGood listening skillsGood understanding of the sales process to align actions with Sales Managers\n\nCareers Privacy Statement***Keysight is an Equal Opportunity Employer.***"}
